Tk/MinMaxScale version 0.08
===========================

Tk::MinMaxScale - Two Scale(s) to get a (min, max) values pair

CHANGES from 0.07

	- compatibility with Tk804.xxx (dash before option).

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

